description:

When you want to wear other clothes for her, just add "alice_halo", and lower the weight of LORA and raise the weight of clothes.

With "idol _alice", you can generate alice of idol clothing, but because the number of relevant pictures is not enough, it can play an obvious role in the version with higher numbers, and the generalization ability is general.

When you want to take off her clothes or make some NSFW, use the tag "zhuo".
